<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>회원정보수정</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="//t1.daumcdn.net/mapjsapi/bundle/postcode/prod/postcode.v2.js"></script>
  <script src="../js/join.js"></script>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/join.css">
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container mt-3 formsizing company-register">
    <img src="../images/codeppl_remove.png" alt="코드피플_회원가입이미지"
      style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block;" />

    <form action="../js/join.js" id="join">
      <div class="mb-3 mt-3">
        <label>아이디</label> <br>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="id" name="id" disabled>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-3 mt-3">
          <label>비밀번호</label> <br>
          <label class="la2" for="pass">*&nbsp;비밀번호는 8~16자로 영문 대 소문자, 숫자, 특수문자로 이루어져야 합니다.</label>
          <input type="password" class="form-control" id="pass" name="pass" required>
          <span class="error_next_box green" id="pswd1Msg-green" style="display:none" aria-live="assertive">나쁘지않네요.</span>
          <span class="error_next_box" id="pswd1Msg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">8~16자 영문 대 소문자, 숫자, 특수문자를
            사용하세요.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3 mt-3">
        <label>비밀번호 재확인</label> <br>
        <!-- <label class="la2" for="pass">*&nbsp;비밀번호를 재확인합니다.</label> -->
        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="pass2" name="pass2" required>
        <span class="error_next_box" id="pswd2Msg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다.</span>
        <span class="error_next_box green" id="pswd2Msg-green" style="display:none" aria-live="assertive">비밀번호가 일치합니다!</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>이름</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" required>
        <span class="error_next_box" id="nameMsg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">한글과 영문 대 소문자를 사용하세요.
          (특수기호, 공백 사용 불가)</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label>전화번호</label>
          <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="tel" name="tel" required>
          <span class="error_next_box" id="telMsg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">휴대폰 번호를 다시 확인해 주세요.
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>이메일 주소</label>
        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required>
        <span class="error_next_box" id="emailMsg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">이메일 주소를 다시 확인해 주세요.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>생년월일</label>
        <input type="date" class="form-control" id="bir" name="bir">
      </div>


          <div class="mb-3 zip">
            <label>우편번호</label>
            <div class="zipInput">
              <input type="text" class="form-control zip" id="postCode" name="postCode" disabled>
              <input type="button" onclick="execDaumPostcode()" value="우편번호 검색" />
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label>주소1</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id=roadAddress name="roadAddress" disabled>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label>주소2</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="detailAddress" name="detailAddress">
          </div>


      <div class="btn-center-box">
        <a href="./home.html"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg  mx-2"
            onclick="alert('회원정보 수정이 성공적으로 완료되었습니다!')">수정하기</button></a>
        <a href="../htmltest/mainMypage.html"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg  mx-2">취소</button></a>
      </div>

    </form>
  </div>

</body>
</html>